{
  "texts": [
    "All excluded papers were labeled by at least two reviewers, and any conflicts were discussed between reviewers and resolved by a third reviewer.",
    "This phase resulted in the exclusion of 96 articles.",
    "We note that the main reason why relatively many of the initial hits were excluded refers to the fact that articles did not test empirically for bias.",
    "This points out the deficit of empirical studies, despite the wide discussion of these issues.",
    "Eventually, 116 articles were included for the scoping review."
  ]
}